    {
      "chinese": "男生從三歲起跟隨父輩到山上打獵，四歲幫打獵的長輩背裝食物的蔞，十歲左右參加打耳祭，以照顧營火為由，在山上待一至三個夜晚，訓練膽量。",
      "ab": "Maqa bananaz tu uva’az maca tauna qamisan na kitnga’in lavilavi munludunqanup, maca pat’in qamisan na kadangaz’in mama’ i kokonun kumbu’un palangan tu na paka’un ni madadaing’az, maca macan’in qamisan na pinhamu’unin malaq tainga’ tu sinluc’an, malavi munludunta paltini’un tau tu qani’an pasaipuk’un ni sapuz, maupata a madadaing’az patanam mi uva’az bananaz.",
